I made this tonight for supper. It was fantastic and very quick. I couldn't find tostadas so I pan-fried corn tortillas. Using the canned refried beans and jarred salsa made the dish so easy. The combination of flavors and textures are wonderful and the goat cheese is a must. I'm always looking for dishes that are fast but have big flavor. This is one of them.

